data.description: NO HOA! Explore this charming property located in a convenient neighborhood that combines practicality and style. Nestled in a popular community, this home offers a cozy and functional living space with easy freeway or downtown access. Inside, you'll find a well-designed layout with a large kitchen and good size backyard. The outdoor area features a patio and plenty of room for the dogs or kids.  The kitchen is perfect for everyday cooking, and the living room offers a comfortable spot by the fireplace. The master bedroom provides a private retreat with a balcony that looks to the north with mountain views. There's ample parking with a garage and a wide side yard.  Don't miss the opportunity to view this home and make it your own.
